==============
WHY THIS LICENSING APPROACH?
==============

Our goals are:
- To enable individual creators and open-source communities to use freely
- To ensure SaaS service improvements contribute back to the community
- To provide a legal licensing path for enterprises needing closed-source commercialization
- To protect the original authorship and prevent misrepresentation

